SUMMARY:Engineering with AI: Tools & Workflows for Next Gen Development Workshop
DESCRIPTION:Modern Web (Triangle)\nJoin this immersive workshop to learn how modern engineering teams are integrating AI into everyday workflows. Through hands-on sessions\, you’ll explore proven frameworks and practical AI playbooks that make code reviews faster\, documentation smoother\, and planning more strategic.\n\nYou’ll leave with battle-tested frameworks\, real experience\, and a concrete plan to bring AI tools and automation into your daily dev process.\n\n**[This is a ticketed event. Seats are limited! Learn more here!](https://ai.thisdot.co/workshops)**\n\n**Use code MODERNWEB at checkout for $50 tickets!**
